  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview:</strong><br>Brace yourself for an epic battle of brains and firepower in <i>Doomsday Tower Defense</i>, a fast-paced and strategic top-down game blending action, simulation, and strategy. With colorful 2D visuals and a dark, thrilling atmosphere, players must defend humanity's last stronghold against endless waves of zombies. Build, strategize, and manage resources to outwit and outlast the zombie apocalypse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/e9a378dcefad126f66d38b758875a264.poster.avif?t=1740555059\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/e9a378dcefad126f66d38b758875a264.webm?t=1740555059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/e9a378dcefad126f66d38b758875a264.mp4?t=1740555059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Strategic Defenses:</strong> Construct towers along designated spots beside the zombie path to stop the horde.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/ee560725ecb9b9e9ee113f651d3db1d8.avif?t=1740555059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras_big/ee560725ecb9b9e9ee113f651d3db1d8.avif?t=1740555059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn and Spend Wisely:</strong> Gain coins by killing zombies and invest in building and upgrading towers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/ac915a1c92f398611ccdaa62212a64c0.avif?t=1740555059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras_big/ac915a1c92f398611ccdaa62212a64c0.avif?t=1740555059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Zombie Types:</strong> Encounter different kinds of zombies, each with unique abilities and challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/f454e35de88fcc93bbf273b88c949f6c.avif?t=1740555059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras_big/f454e35de88fcc93bbf273b88c949f6c.avif?t=1740555059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Towers:</strong> Unlock and deploy various tower types, each with specialized strengths to adapt to your strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/3bb177243c96f898a64f390929aee046.avif?t=1740555059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras_big/3bb177243c96f898a64f390929aee046.avif?t=1740555059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wave Survival:</strong> Survive through increasingly difficult waves of zombies, with a progress bar marking your journey to victory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/2407023b5d605084267f18a9c9851b9b.avif?t=1740555059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras_big/2407023b5d605084267f18a9c9851b9b.avif?t=1740555059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Progression:</strong> Complete 20 levels and unlock new, harder challenges. The higher you climb, the tougher the apocalypse becomes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/3e1abceecee5c159970f81430b3aa7e6.avif?t=1740555059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras_big/3e1abceecee5c159970f81430b3aa7e6.avif?t=1740555059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Basecamp Defense:</strong> Protect your basecamp at all costs. Let too many zombies through, and it's game over!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/94fb314ddef76964ccd1cb1c7a5e555a.avif?t=1740555059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras_big/94fb314ddef76964ccd1cb1c7a5e555a.avif?t=1740555059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong><br>Start by setting up towers in limited spots beside a predetermined path. Zombies spawn at the starting point and march relentlessly toward your basecamp. Your goal? Stop them before they reach the end and reduce your base’s health. As you progress, face diverse zombie types and unlock advanced towers to refine your defense strategy. The game ends when the zombie wave bar is cleared, signaling your triumph—or your basecamp falls.<br>Get ready for an addictive mix of logic, management, and shoot-'em-up action. Can you survive the doomsday and protect the last bastion of humanity?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview:</strong><br>Brace yourself for an epic battle of brains and firepower in <i>Doomsday Tower Defense</i>, a fast-paced and strategic top-down game blending action, simulation, and strategy. With colorful 2D visuals and a dark, thrilling atmosphere, players must defend humanity's last stronghold against endless waves of zombies. Build, strategize, and manage resources to outwit and outlast the zombie apocalypse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/e9a378dcefad126f66d38b758875a264.poster.avif?t=1740555059\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/e9a378dcefad126f66d38b758875a264.webm?t=1740555059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/e9a378dcefad126f66d38b758875a264.mp4?t=1740555059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Strategic Defenses:</strong> Construct towers along designated spots beside the zombie path to stop the horde.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/ee560725ecb9b9e9ee113f651d3db1d8.avif?t=1740555059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras_big/ee560725ecb9b9e9ee113f651d3db1d8.avif?t=1740555059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn and Spend Wisely:</strong> Gain coins by killing zombies and invest in building and upgrading towers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/ac915