 The higher you climb, the tougher the apocalypse becomes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/3e1abceecee5c159970f81430b3aa7e6.avif?t=1740555059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras_big/3e1abceecee5c159970f81430b3aa7e6.avif?t=1740555059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Basecamp Defense:</strong> Protect your basecamp at all costs. Let too many zombies through, and it's game over!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras/94fb314ddef76964ccd1cb1c7a5e555a.avif?t=1740555059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365120/extras_big/94fb314ddef76964ccd1cb1c7a5e555a.avif?t=1740555059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong><br>Start by setting up towers in limited spots beside a predetermined path. Zombies spawn at the starting point and march relentlessly toward your basecamp. Your goal? Stop them before they reach the end and reduce your base’s health. As you progress, face diverse zombie types and unlock advanced towers to refine your defense strategy. The game ends when the zombie wave bar is cleared, signaling your triumph—or your basecamp falls.<br>Get ready for an addictive mix of logic, management, and shoot-'em-up action. Can you survive the doomsday and protect the last bastion of humanity?</p>",
